    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined that the single-condition limitation does not invalidate the credibility conclusion given the direct correspondence between the validation activity and the COU, the multi-laboratory experimental dataset, and the quantitative validation metrics all within acceptance bounds. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the regulatory submission.",
